@startuml
actor Customer
participant Frontend
participant "DRF API" as API
database PostgreSQL

Customer -> Frontend: Checkout cart
Frontend -> API: POST /api/orders
API -> PostgreSQL: Validate stock
alt Stock available
  API -> PostgreSQL: Create order + decrease stock
  API --> Frontend: 201 Created
  Frontend --> Customer: Order confirmation
else Out of stock
  API --> Frontend: 400 Bad Request
  Frontend --> Customer: Show stock error
end
@enduml
